---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="贡献剧本 · 喜剧档案">
  <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">贡献剧本</h1>
  <p class="mb-6 text-sm text-neutral-700">
    在 YouTube / B 站上发现想分享的漫才？填下面表单（不需要懂 git），
    维护者审核后会自动转写并加进档案。
  </p>

  <form id="submit-form" class="space-y-4 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-md p-5">
    <div>
      <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1">视频 URL <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
      <input type="url" name="url" required placeholder="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=..."
             class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-neutral-300 rounded text-sm" />
    </div>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1">组合名 <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
        <input type="text" name="group" required placeholder="令和ロマン"
               class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-neutral-300 rounded text-sm" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1">组合 slug <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
        <input type="text" name="group_slug" required placeholder="reiwaroman" pattern="[a-z0-9\-]+"
               class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-neutral-300 rounded text-sm" />
        <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 mt-1">仅小写字母、数字、连字符</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1">标签</label>
      <input type="text" name="tags" placeholder="M-1, 2022, 決勝"
             class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-neutral-300 rounded text-sm" />
      <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 mt-1">逗号分隔</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1">敏感度</label>
        <select name="sensitivity" class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-neutral-300 rounded text-sm">
          <option value="normal">normal（一般 UP 主、自频道）</option>
          <option value="high">high（M-1 决赛、电视节目）</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1">语言（可选）</label>
        <input type="text" name="language" placeholder="ja"
               class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-neutral-300 rounded text-sm" />
        <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 mt-1">留空则自动检测</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1">备注</label>
      <textarea name="notes" rows="3" placeholder="任何对审核有帮助的信息"
                class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-neutral-300 rounded text-sm"></textarea>
    </div>
    <button type="submit"
            class="w-full px-4 py-2 bg-neutral-900 text-white rounded font-medium hover:bg-neutral-700 transition">
      在 GitHub 上提交（需要 GH 账号）
    </button>
    <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 text-center">
      点击会跳转到 GitHub 预填好的 issue 页面，确认后提交。
      没有 GH 账号？<a class="underline" href="https://github.com/join" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2 分钟注册</a>。
    </p>
  </form>

  <div class="mt-8 text-sm">
    <h2 class="font-semibold mb-2">其他贡献方式</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 text-neutral-700">
      <li>已有干净文本？<a class="underline" href="https://github.com/manzai-archive/web/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md#b-手写-markdown-pr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">直接提 PR</a></li>
      <li>能跑 Python？<a class="underline" href="https://github.com/manzai-archive/pipeline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">本地跑 pipeline</a></li>
      <li>发现某条剧本有错？<a class="underline" href="https://github.com/manzai-archive/web/issues/new/choose" target="_blank" rel="noopener">报告问题</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <script is:inline>
    document.getElementById('submit-form').addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
      e.preventDefault();
      const f = e.target;
      const v = (n) => f.elements[n].value.trim();
      const body = [
        `### 视频 URL`, v('url'), '',
        `### 组合名 / 表演者`, v('group'), '',
        `### 组合 slug`, v('group_slug'), '',
        `### 标签`, v('tags') || '_未填_', '',
        `### 版权敏感度`, v('sensitivity'), '',
        `### 语言（可选）`, v('language') || '_自动检测_', '',
        `### 备注`, v('notes') || '_无_',
      ].join('\n');
      const url = new URL('https://github.com/manzai-archive/web/issues/new');
      url.searchParams.set('template', 'submit-script.yml');
      url.searchParams.set('title', `[提交] ${v('group')} — `);
      url.searchParams.set('url', v('url'));
      url.searchParams.set('group', v('group'));
      url.searchParams.set('group_slug', v('group_slug'));
      url.searchParams.set('tags', v('tags'));
      url.searchParams.set('sensitivity', v('sensitivity'));
      url.searchParams.set('language', v('language'));
      url.searchParams.set('notes', v('notes'));
      window.open(url.toString(), '_blank');
    });
  </script>
</Base>
